name: Chelsea
summary: Chelsea's recent run includes a 3-1 victory over FC Astana in the UEFA Conference League on December 12, 2024, and a thrilling 4-3 win over Tottenham on December 8, 2024. These victories have propelled Chelsea to second place in the league table. In the match against Tottenham, Jadon Sancho played a key role, while the match against Astana saw a number of Academy players join Chelsea's traveling squad. Chelsea manager Enzo Maresca has emphasized the importance of maintaining momentum after the win over Tottenham. Meanwhile, authorities are investigating the fatal shooting of a woman in Chelsea, with her estranged husband charged with murder. Residents in the area have also reported a mysterious odor. Joao Felix's absence from the Conference League match against Astana has been attributed to an unspecified "issue" at Chelsea.

name: No Good Deed
summary: Netflix's new limited series, "No Good Deed," has garnered a mixed reception upon its premiere. Some critics praise the show's dark and twisted plot, predicting it will become a popular hit. However, others find the show's premise, which revolves around a couple's nightmarish home search, to be more punishing than entertaining. Despite the contrasting opinions, the series has received recognition for its star-studded cast, including Lisa Kudrow and Ray Romano, and for the stunning Los Angeles dream home that serves as the backdrop for the unsettling events. Ultimately, the show's ending has sparked discussions about the true nature of the events that unfold, leaving viewers grappling with unanswered questions and the possibility of a deeper mystery.

name: Isaac Guerendo
summary: 49ers running back Isaac Guerendo has been diagnosed with a foot sprain, according to coach Kyle Shanahan. The injury raises questions about Guerendo's availability for Thursday's game against the Rams. Guerendo, who is expected to handle a "heavy workload" in the absence of Christian McCaffrey, is considered a potential starter for the 49ers. Despite the injury, Guerendo plans to play against the Rams. The team is still evaluating Guerendo's status, but he has been declared active for the game. Guerendo is not overly concerned about the injury, which he sustained in the 49ers' win over the Bears. Other key players, Nick Bosa and Dre Greenlaw, are also active for the 49ers on Thursday night.

summary: President Biden's recent executive actions regarding clemency have sparked significant attention. Biden issued 39 pardons and commuted the sentences of over 1,500 individuals, a record number for a single day. These actions have raised questions about the President's willingness to exercise presidential powers in novel ways, as he weighs granting pardons to a wider range of individuals, including his son, Hunter Biden. The pardons and commutations have been met with both praise and criticism, with some calling for more clemency while others express concerns about the potential implications.

name: YouTube TV price increase
summary: YouTube TV has announced a significant price increase, raising its monthly charge by 14 percent to $82.99. This move has sent shockwaves through the streaming industry, as it signals a shift away from the era of streaming services as a frugal alternative to traditional cable. The price hike, which takes effect in 2025, has been attributed to the rising cost of content. This increase follows a previous price adjustment in 2022, making YouTube TV one of the more expensive streaming options available. Industry analysts suggest that the price hike may prompt subscribers to re-evaluate their streaming choices and potentially consider more affordable options.

name: Virgen de Guadalupe
summary: Various news outlets are highlighting the celebration of the Feast of Our Lady of Guadalupe. In Houston, overcrowding concerns have prompted vendors to leave the popular East End Virgen de Guadalupe celebration. Telemundo 52 in Los Angeles will broadcast special coverage of the event. In Corpus Christi, the celebration has been passed down through generations in honor of La Virgen de Guadalupe. The University of San Diego hosted its own celebration. Telemundo will air a live special called 'Mañanitas a la Virgen de Guadalupe' on December 11th. KPRC Click2Houston explores the significance of El Día de la Virgen de Guadalupe to Houstonians. Telemundo Texas will celebrate with 'Las Mañanitas a la Virgen.' The Catholic community gathered to mark the Feast of Our Lady of Guadalupe, while pilgrims in Santa Rosa prepared for a 12-mile journey to honor the Virgin. Despite cold weather, Laredo held its own celebration.

name: Okami
summary: The beloved action-adventure game "Okami" is finally getting a sequel. The announcement was made at The Game Awards 2024, with Hideki Kamiya, the original game's director, returning to lead the project. The sequel is being developed by a revived Clover Studio, the studio that created the original game. The announcement has been met with excitement from fans, who have been eagerly anticipating a sequel for years.

name: Gukesh
summary: Indian chess prodigy Gukesh Dommaraju, at the age of 18, has achieved an extraordinary feat by becoming the youngest-ever undisputed world chess champion. In a thrilling World Chess Championship final against Ding Liren, Gukesh pulled off a remarkable upset to secure the coveted title. Despite initially trailing in the match, Gukesh fought back with determination, ultimately forcing Ding to make a costly blunder that sealed his victory. This historic achievement marks a significant milestone in the young chess prodigy's career and a proud moment for India in the world of chess.

name: Voice of America
summary: Former US President Donald Trump has nominated Kari Lake, a former Republican gubernatorial candidate from Arizona, to lead Voice of America (VOA). VOA is a US government-funded international broadcasting service. Trump's decision has raised concerns among some who believe Lake's previous attacks on the media could make her an unfit leader for VOA. Lake has previously accused mainstream media outlets of being "fake news" and has promoted conspiracy theories.
